    "bio_summary": "Bastiaan de Nooijer, also known as Piece Wise is a 25-year-old Dutch music producer born in Spain and raised in Africa. Piece Wise has spent the majority of his life living in Africa, in countries such as Cameroon, Senegal, Mozambique & Mali where he has gained valuable life experiences. His musical journey began in 2012 when he first experimented with electronic music production. Over time, Piece Wise has developed his unique sound and has tied his main focus to electronic dance music.  <a href",
